Common Issues
Navigation & Routing


Q: My route is not loading or showing incorrect directions

Ensure you have a stable internet connection
Check that location services are enabled: Settings â†’ Privacy & Security â†’ Location Services â†’ TruckNav Pro
Verify your truck dimensions are set correctly in Settings
Try restarting the app


Q: Voice guidance is not working

Check voice volume in Settings â†’ Navigation â†’ Voice Volume
Ensure your device volume is turned up
Verify background audio permission is enabled
Check if "Do Not Disturb" mode is active


Q: App says my truck can't use this route

This is normal - TruckNav Pro uses TomTom truck routing to avoid restricted roads
Check your truck height, weight, and hazmat settings in Settings â†’ Truck Specifications
The route may have low bridges, weight restrictions, or hazmat prohibitions
Location & GPS
Q: My location is not accurate or not showing

Enable "Precise Location" for best accuracy: Settings â†’ Privacy & Security â†’ Location Services â†’ TruckNav Pro â†’ Precise Location
Ensure you're not in a tunnel, parking garage, or area with poor GPS signal
Try toggling Airplane Mode on/off to reset GPS
Restart your device


Q: Background navigation stops working

Enable "Always" location permission: Settings â†’ Privacy & Security â†’ Location Services â†’ TruckNav Pro â†’ Always
Ensure Low Power Mode is disabled (it restricts background activity)
Check that Background App Refresh is enabled for TruckNav Pro
Subscriptions

Q: I purchased Pro/Premium but still see locked features

Pull down on the Settings screen to refresh subscription status
Tap "Restore Purchases" in Settings â†’ Account
Sign out and sign back in to your account
If issue persists, contact support with your purchase receipt

Q: How do I cancel my subscription?

Open Settings app on your iPhone â†’ [Your Name] â†’ Subscriptions
Select TruckNav Pro
Tap "Cancel Subscription"
Note: Canceling will take effect at the end of your current billing period

Q: I was charged twice

Check your Apple ID subscriptions to verify only one active subscription exists
Contact Apple Support for billing issues: https://support.apple.com/billing
Email us with your receipt for assistance: support@trucknavpro.com
Weather & Traffic

Q: Weather widget not showing data

Ensure you have an active internet connection
Location services must be enabled
Weather data requires a valid GPS signal
Try pulling down to refresh the widget

Q: Traffic data is outdated or not showing

Traffic requires Pro or Premium subscription
Ensure you have an active internet connection
Traffic data updates every 2-5 minutes
Some rural areas may have limited traffic data
Account & Sync

Q: My saved routes disappeared

Ensure you're signed into the same account
Check your internet connection for cloud sync
Saved routes sync may take a few minutes
Free tier is limited to 5 saved routes

Q: Settings not syncing across devices

Sign in with the same account on all devices
Enable cloud sync in Settings
Ensure both devices have internet connection
Try signing out and back in
