Troubleshooting Steps
General Issues
Force quit the app (swipe up from bottom, swipe TruckNav Pro up)
Restart the app
Check for app updates in the App Store
Restart your iPhone
Reinstall the app (Note: May lose local data)
Crash on Launch
Ensure iOS is up to date: Settings â†’ General â†’ Software Update
Free up storage space: Settings â†’ General â†’ iPhone Storage
Reinstall TruckNav Pro from the App Store
If issue persists, contact support with crash details
Performance Issues
Close other apps running in the background
Disable Low Power Mode temporarily
Clear app cache: Settings â†’ TruckNav Pro â†’ Clear Cache
Ensure you have at least 500MB free storage
Restart your device
