Third-Party Services
TruckNav Pro uses the following services:

MapBox: Mapping and navigation
TomTom: Truck-specific routing
OpenWeather: Weather data
Supabase: Cloud storage and authentication
RevenueCat: Subscription management
For issues specific to these services, we'll coordinate with them on your behalf.

